    <briefdescription>
<para>Low-level publisher that writes raw bytes to a shared memory ring buffer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Creates a shared memory region at <computeroutput>/dev/shm/conduit_{topic}</computeroutput> and manages a lock-free SPMC ring buffer for zero-copy message delivery. Use the typed Publisher&lt;T&gt; wrapper for type-safe publishing.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>conduit::Publisher </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
